Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为众生之死献上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为可悲之灵予以嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,缇奥 老师 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,天轮 不及回转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,灵魂既失容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的 她都已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}徘徊现世 不渡生死之门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}何不于两界之间开启生诞之门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你不和我作对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}祓除死念 重结绽放之灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我就用魔法复活香织 我的建议如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 南云
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得他们和生前没什么两样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,人都死了还能怎么办嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,至少变得像他们一样也不错对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 还可以对香织为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为此可不能少了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大意失荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一样吗 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}糟了 快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心情 目的 我都懒得听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么事的话 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,南云
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你 要是没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,香织就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别怪别人 你的失败只能怪你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,从不曾想担起任何责任的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一条纯粹的败犬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要杀了你 我一定要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你先试试还能不能活下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,至少灵魂的归位已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不过接下来就要花点时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最好能借助月的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,已经坚持不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴们的性命不重要了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,城墙外十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,传送门外百万魔物严阵以待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕你们再强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也不可能一边保护着所有人不停战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么时候说过王国和这些人是我同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想打仗随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 要是你敢妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见 我会毁灭你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这份耻辱 我一定会让你偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我以神之名起誓 我一定会让你尸骨无存
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,始 那个傻大个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 那个死垃圾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,南云 香织 香织她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,希娅 香织就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,香织小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,缇奥 给月她们带路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老师也麻烦帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 我们去山顶 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小爱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小爱老师去救香织吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 园部同学 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,八重槛 别泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我们 等我们的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会让你再见到香织
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,南云
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你都这样了 以后谁来替我们解决麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 新的旅程
Comment: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------OP-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:12.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:18.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:24.06,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:30.49,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:35.91,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:39.66,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.50,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:47.42,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:53.38,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:59.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:04.52,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.77,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:13.11,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Comment: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:04.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,------------------ED------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆为虚空一场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破灭的希望　虚伪的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身体的伤口深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅是我　你也背负同样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得谁人原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕怀中相拥　徒留轮廓难辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘愿承伤不曾犹豫的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹒跚　忍痛离开你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}几步对错　令我身负百孔千疮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形单影只渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　谁人不曾拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
